{"type":"message","id":"1a807633","parentId":"6bfc2681","timestamp":"2026-04-05T06:15:33.316Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_839052b815f643118135d193","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- Fetching skill\nelite-longterm-memory  Elite Longterm Memory\nSummary: Ultimate AI agent memory system for Cursor, Claude, ChatGPT & Copilot. WAL protocol + vector search + git-notes + cloud backup. Never lose context again. Vibe-coding ready.\nOwner: nextfrontierbuilds\nCreated: 2026-02-02T16:37:23.398Z\nUpdated: 2026-04-05T03:18:52.291Z\nLatest: 1.2.3\nLicense: MIT-0 (Free to use, modify, and redistribute. No attribution required.)\nTags: ai=0.1.0, clawdbot=0.1.0, latest=1.2.3, long-term=0.1.0, memory=0.1.0, openclaw=0.1.0, persistence=0.1.0\nSelected: 1.2.3\nSelected At: 2026-02-11T08:37:00.241Z\nChangelog: - Expanded description and keywords for improved discoverability, highlighting ChatGPT, Copilot, Cursor, and develope...\nSecurity: SUSPICIOUS\nWarnings: yes\nChecked: 2026-04-05T03:18:52.094Z\nModel: gpt-5-mini\nFiles:\nREADME.md  5.5KB  17c0c112c1363fe9568fdbd10674660aa6755f6ba454f5d919bc332a34c0c653  text/markdown\nSKILL.md  12KB  56bb341604f951985e451df450744d1d78cd9ba905b6df8952084343b35a95b3  text/markdown\nbin/elite-memory.js  4.8KB  a937f5aab36c4b6ee0760a4ebe7499aab204f663b97c71da8e066b206dcc9e2d  text/javascript\npackage.json  1.3KB  188612db5a262a29f2ee6f68ddb138597966f5e5e46a8856de75a23aad76450f  application/json"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1473,"aggregated":"- Fetching skill\nelite-longterm-memory  Elite Longterm Memory\nSummary: Ultimate AI agent memory system for Cursor, Claude, ChatGPT & Copilot. WAL protocol + vector search + git-notes + cloud backup. Never lose context again. Vibe-coding ready.\nOwner: nextfrontierbuilds\nCreated: 2026-02-02T16:37:23.398Z\nUpdated: 2026-04-05T03:18:52.291Z\nLatest: 1.2.3\nLicense: MIT-0 (Free to use, modify, and redistribute. No attribution required.)\nTags: ai=0.1.0, clawdbot=0.1.0, latest=1.2.3, long-term=0.1.0, memory=0.1.0, openclaw=0.1.0, persistence=0.1.0\nSelected: 1.2.3\nSelected At: 2026-02-11T08:37:00.241Z\nChangelog: - Expanded description and keywords for improved discoverability, highlighting ChatGPT, Copilot, Cursor, and develope...\nSecurity: SUSPICIOUS\nWarnings: yes\nChecked: 2026-04-05T03:18:52.094Z\nModel: gpt-5-mini\nFiles:\nREADME.md  5.5KB  17c0c112c1363fe9568fdbd10674660aa6755f6ba454f5d919bc332a34c0c653  text/markdown\nSKILL.md  12KB  56bb341604f951985e451df450744d1d78cd9ba905b6df8952084343b35a95b3  text/markdown\nbin/elite-memory.js  4.8KB  a937f5aab36c4b6ee0760a4ebe7499aab204f663b97c71da8e066b206dcc9e2d  text/javascript\npackage.json  1.3KB  188612db5a262a29f2ee6f68ddb138597966f5e5e46a8856de75a23aad76450f  application/json","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775369733307}}
