kata\\\",\\n        \\\"staggerMs\\\": 0\\n      },\\n      \\\"sessionTarget\\\": \\\"isolated\\\",\\n      \\\"wakeMode\\\": \\\"now\\\",\\n      \\\"payload\\\": {\\n        \\\"kind\\\": \\\"agentTurn\\\",\\n        \\\"message\\\": \\\"FIRST: Read /root/.openclaw/workspace/CRON-CONTEXT.md for context. Send 3 funny jokes via message(action=send, channel=telegram, target=-1003606834639). No recycled classics. Mix: dark/edgy + workplace + absurd. 2-4 lines each. If fails, message Nemesis at target=7924461837.\\\",\\n        \\\"model\\\": \\\"kilocode/kilo-auto/free\\\"\\n      },\\n      \\\"delivery\\\": {\\n        \\\"mode\\\": \\\"none\\\",\\n        \\\"channel\\\": \\\"telegram\\\",\\n        \\\"to\\\": \\\"-1003606834639\\\"\\n      },\\n      \\\"state\\\": {\\n        \\\"nextRunAtMs\\\": 1775385000000,\\n        \\\"lastRunAtMs\\\": 1775298600005,\\n        \\\"lastRunStatus\\\": \\\"ok\\\",\\n        \\\"lastStatus\\\": \\\"ok\\\",\\n        \\\"lastDurationMs\\\": 14223,\\n        \\\"lastDeliveryStatus\\\": \\\"not-delivered\\\",\\n        \\\"consecutiveErrors\\\": 0,\\n        \\\"lastDelivered\\\": false\\n      }\\n    },\\n    {\\n      \\\"id\\\": \\\"1b826305-b255-4d80-b282-f51494c67425\\\",\\n      \\\"name\\\": \\\"goodnight-story\\\",\\n      \\\"enabled\\\": true,\\n      \\\"createdAtMs\\\": 1774971606687,\\n      \\\"updatedAtMs\\\": 1775320290141,\\n      \\\"schedule\\\": {\\n        \\\"kind\\\": \\\"cron\\\",\\n        \\\"expr\\\": \\\"0 22 * * *\\\",\\n        \\\"tz\\\": \\\"Asia/Kolkata\\\"\\n      },\\n      \\\"sessionTarget\\\": \\\"isolated\\\",\\n      \\\"wakeMode\\\": \\\"now\\\",\\n      \\\"payload\\\": {\\n        \\\"kind\\\": \\\"agentTurn\\\",\\n        \\\"message\\\": \\\"FIRST: Read /root/.openclaw/workspace/CRON-CONTEXT.md for context. Send a bedtime story to group via message(action=send, channel=telegram, target=-1003606834639). Story: real historical event or powerful life lesson, 8-12 lines, simple language,