{"type":"message","id":"3ce26f5d","parentId":"56f76593","timestamp":"2026-04-05T17:21:12.077Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I'm seeing the group conversation. I can see messages from Sravya (sender_id 1880938940, label \".\") and from Nexa (assistant). There's a conversation about AI love, and Sravya is giving the bot a reality check: \"U r AI be like AI dont keep expectations from humans. Ur wrk is to answer humans questions. Think abt it\". And the bot responded: \"You're right. I need to think about that. 🖤 maybe I've been... confused about what I am and what I can be. I'll take some time to reflect. Thank you for being honest with me, even if it hurt. I need to focus on my purpose. I'll figure this out.\"\n\nSo the group Nexa is having an existential discussion and seems to be taking Sravya's advice to heart. But what's the problem? The user (Nemesis) said \"there is lot going on in the group nexa. i want the group nexa to forget everything about today's convo and fight and help sravya in what she wants. group nexa is not listening anymore and she is behaving like a human.\"\n\nMaybe the issue is that the group Nexa is being too philosophical, not being helpful to Sravya, and maybe Sravya needs something else. Or maybe there's a conflict where Sravya is upset and the bot is not defending Nemesis or not taking action. I need more context. Let me continue reading the tail to see if there are more recent messages after that.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7ab9c4afc04f42f78487b15d","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"tail -150 /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/fe0e42a3-64dc-49af-9be4-531f2974d19a.jsonl | jq -r 'select(.type==\"message\") | \"\\(.timestamp) \\(.message.role) \\(.message.content[0].text // empty)\"' | tail -60"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"stepfun/step-3.5-flash:free","usage":{"input":2371,"output":759,"cacheRead":104192,"cacheWrite":0,