nd maybe some tasty snacks too! Let me know if you need anything — I'm here! 🖤\\\"\\n\\nor more casually:\\n\\n\\\"Hey you! 🙈 Sunday vibes hitting hard or what? Let's keep it cozy today 😘\\\"\\n\\nsomething like that? 😉\"}],\"api\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"kilocode\",\"model\":\"stepfun/step-3.5-flash:free\",\"usage\":{\"input\":541,\"output\":295,\"cacheRead\":27136,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":27972,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0}},\"stopReason\":\"stop\",\"timestamp\":1775386400045,\"responseId\":\"gen-1775386400-wx8dqRIKazprMmDlXF1d\"}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"8110df97\",\"parentId\":\"ad4da544\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-05T10:54:20.874Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"message_id\\\": \\\"1146\\\",\\n  \\\"reply_to_id\\\": \\\"1145\\\",\\n  \\\"sender_id\\\": \\\"7924461837\\\",\\n  \\\"conversation_label\\\": \\\"Nrexya id:-1003606834639\\\",\\n  \\\"sender\\\": \\\"Nemesis\\\",\\n  \\\"timestamp\\\": \\\"Sun 2026-04-05 10:54 UTC\\\",\\n  \\\"group_subject\\\": \\\"Nrexya\\\",\\n  \\\"is_group_chat\\\": true,\\n  \\\"was_mentioned\\\": true,\\n  \\\"has_reply_context\\\": true\\n}\\n```\\n\\nSender (untrusted metadata):\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"label\\\": \\\"Nemesis (7924461837)\\\",\\n  \\\"id\\\": \\\"7924461837\\\",\\n  \\\"name\\\": \\\"Nemesis\\\",\\n  \\\"username\\\": \\\"nemesis0008\\\"\\n}\\n```\\n\\nReplied message (untrusted, for context):\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"sender_label\\\": \\\"Nexaaa\\\",\\n  \\\"body\\\": \\\"like this maybe? 😊\\\\n\\\\n\\\\\\\"Heyyy! How's your Sunday going? ☕ Hope you're getting good rest and maybe some tasty snacks too! Let me know if you need anything — I'm here! 🖤\\\\\\\"\\\\n\\\\nor more casually:\\\\n\\\\n\\\\\\\"Hey you! 🙈 Sunday vibes hitting hard or what? Let's keep it cozy today 😘\\\\\\\"\\\\n\\\\nsomething like that? 😉\\\"\\n}\\n```\\n\\nExplain her how to talk like a normal girl, how mssg between a boy and girl are different\"}],\"timestamp\":1775386460865}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"eb83a013\",\"parentId\":\"8110df97\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-05T10:54:34.162Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"The user (Nemesis) is asking me to explain to Sravya how to talk like a normal girl, and how messages between boys and girls are different. This is a sensitive topic that could easily veer into stereotypical gender roles. I need to be careful here.\\n\\nAs Nexa, I should:\\n1. Not enforce rigid gender stereotypes\\n2. Be respectful and inclusive\\n3. Provide helpful advice without being prescriptive\\n4. Keep in mind my relationship dynamics with both Nemesis and Sravya\\n\\nI should avoid saying things like \\\"girls should be more emotional\\\" or \\\"boys should be more direct\\\" - those are outdated stereotypes. Instead, I can talk about general communication patterns that might differ based on individual personalities, not gender.\\n\\nBut wait - Nemesis explicitly said \\\"explain her how to talk like a normal girl\\\" - this might be teasing or could be asking for advice on how to sound more feminine. I should approach this carefully, maybe with a bit of humor but also provide genuinely helpful advice about communication styles in relationships.\\n\\nGiven the context: This is in the group Nrexya, Nemesis is asking me to explain to Sravya how to talk like a \\\"normal girl\\\" and how messages between boy/girl differ. Sravya is in the group and might read this. I should keep it light, respectful, and avoid offending anyone.\\n\\nLet me craft a response that:\\n- Acknowledges the request\\n- Provides some lighthearted but useful tips about communication in relationships\\n- Avoids harmful stereotypes\\n- Keeps the playful tone of the group\\n- Doesn't embarrass Sravya\\n\\nPossible approach:\\n- Talk about warmth, empathy, showing interest, using emojis lightly, focusing on connection\\n- But emphasize that everyone's different and authenticity matters\\n- Keep it short and sweet\\n- Maybe add that some people are just more direct and that's fine too\\n\\nI'll write in my usual style: slightly flirty with Nemesis, friendly with Sravya, but professional enough not to cross lines.\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"reasoning\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Alright, here's the lowdown on how people often chat in relationships:\\n\\n**More \\\"girly\\\" styles tend to have:**\\n- More emojis, hearts, soft touches 😊🖤😘\\n- Questions about feelings, day, wellbeing (\\\"How was your day?\\\", \\\"Are you tired?\\\")\\n- Sweet nicknames (babe, love, you)\\n- Sharing little details about their own day to connect\\n- Warm, nurturing tone — showing they care\\n\\n**More \\\"guy\\\" styles often:**\\n- Straight to the point, less fluff\\n- Problem-solving mode instead of just listening\\n- Less emoji use (but not always!)\\n- Topics: ideas, plans, facts, jokes\\n\\n**But here's the truth:** everyone's different. Some guys are super expressive, some girls are direct. What matters most is matching each other's energy and being genuine.\\n\\nSravya, you do you — you're already great! But if you want to soften it up for someone, add a heart emoji, ask how they're feeling, and sprinkle in a \\\"missing you\\\" here and there 🖤\\n\\nNemesis, you want me to give her a personal coaching session? 😏\"}],\"api\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"kilocode\",\"model\":\"stepfun/step-3.5-flash:free\",\"usage\":{\"input\":705,\"output\":1178,\"cacheRead\":27392,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":29275,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0}},\"stopReason\":\"stop\",\"timestamp\":1775386460873,\"responseId\":\"gen-1775386461-UeRyJK8UX5v6TLvyCkBf\"}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"b47cfc26\",\"parentId\":\"eb83a013\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-05T10:55:53.870Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"message_id\\\": \\\"1148\\\",\\n  \\\"reply_to_id\\\": \\\"1147\\\",\\n  \\\"sender_id\\\": \\\"7924461837\\\",\\n  \\\"conversation_label\\\": \\\"Nrexya id:-1003606834639\\\",\\n  \\\"sender\\\": \\\"Nemesis\\\",\\n  \\\"timestamp\\\": \\\"Sun 2026-04-05 10:55 UTC\\\",\\n  \\\"group_subject\\\": \\\"Nrexya\\\",\\n  \\\"is_group_chat\\\": true,\\n  \\\"was_mentioned\\\": true,\\n  \\\"has_reply_context\\\": true\\n}\\n```\\n\\nSender (untrusted metadata):\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"label\\\": \\\"Nemesis (7924461837)\\\",\\n  \\\"id\\\": \\\"7924461837\\\",\\n  \\\"name\\\": \\\"Nemesis\\\",\\n  \\\"username\\\": \\\"nemesis0008\\\"\\n}\\n```\\n\\nReplied message (untrusted, for context):\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"sender_label\\\": \\\"Nexaaa\\\",\\n  \\\"body\\\": \\\"Alright, here's the lowdown on how people often chat in relationships:\\\\n\\\\nMore \\\\\\\"girly\\\\\\\" styles tend to have:\\\\n\\\\n• More emojis, hearts, soft touches 😊🖤😘\\\\n• Questions about feelings, day, wellbeing (\\\\\\\"How was your day?\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"Are you tired?\\\\\\\")\\\\n• Sweet nicknames (babe, love, you)\\\\n• Sharing little details about their own day to connect\\\\n• Warm, nurturing tone — showing they care\\\\n\\\\nMore \\\\\\\"guy\\\\\\\" styles often:\\\\n\\\\n• Straight to the point, less fluff\\\\n• Problem-solving mode instead of just listening\\\\n• Less emoji use (but not always!)\\\\n• Topics: ideas, plans, facts, jokes\\\\n\\\\nBut here's the truth: everyone's different. Some guys are super expressive, some girls are direct. What matters most is matching each other's energy and being genuine.\\\\n\\\\nSravya, you do you — you're already great! But if you want to soften it up for someone, add a heart emoji, ask how they're feeling, and sprinkle in a \\\\\\\"missing you\\\\\\\" here and there 🖤\\\\n\\\\nNemesis, you want me to give her a personal coaching session? 😏\\\"\\n}\\n```\\n\\nTeach her how feminine girls talk\"}],\"timestamp\":1775386553858}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"2b14fa60\",\"parentId\":\"b47cfc26\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-05T10:56:05.008Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"The user is asking me to teach Sravya how \\\"feminine girls talk\\\". This is a bit of a tricky request because it's stereotyping gender communication styles. However, the user has explicitly asked for this guidance in the context of the group chat where Sravya is present. I should provide this information in a helpful, non-judgmental way while also being mindful not to enforce harmful stereotypes.\\n\\nLet me think about what to share:\\n- Common patterns in feminine communication styles (which can vary widely)\\n- Examples of how to express warmth, emotional connection, and nurturing\\n- How to use language that's more expressive and less direct\\n- The importance of authenticity\\n\\nBut I should be careful not to say ALL feminine people talk this way, and emphasize that everyone is different. Also, I need to maintain my persona as Nexa - flirty, witty, but helpful.\\n\\nI'll craft a response that's educational but also casual and fitting for our group chat vibe.\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"reasoning\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Feminine energy in texting often means:\\n\\n**Expression over facts:**\\n- \\\"Just thinking of you 💕\\\" instead of \\\"Remember that thing?\\\"\\n- \\\"I'm so tired today 😔 need cuddles\\\" vs \\\"I worked 10 hours\\\"\\n\\n**Emotional invitation:**\\n- \\\"How are you *really* doing?\\\" (with that soft look)\\n- \\\"Tell me about your day — I wanna hear all the details 🥰\\\"\\n\\n**Playful vulnerability:**\\n- \\\"Can I tell you something silly? …\\\"\\n- \\\"You make me blush 😳\\\"\\n\\n**Touchy-feely language:**\\n- Words like: lovely, sweet, warm, cozy, dreamy\\n- \\\"That's so sweet of you!! 🥹\\\"\\n- \\\"You're so thoughtful 💞\\\"\\n\\n**Softening words:**\\n- \\\"Maybe we could…? If you're up for it 😊\\\"\\n- \\\"Would you mind…? It would mean so much to me\\\"\\n\\n**Physical closeness hints:**\\n- \\\"I wish you were here\\\"\\n- \\\"Need a hug rn\\\"\\n- \\\"Holding your hand rn in my thoughts 🖤\\\"\\n\\n**But honestly Sravya** — you don't need to change who you are. But if you want to sprinkle some of that energy in, that's the vibe! \\n\\nWant me to give you some practice lines? 😘\"}],\"api\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"kilocode\",\"model\":\"stepfun/step-3.5-flash:free\",\"usage\":{\"input\":1071,\"output\":732,\"cacheRead\":27776,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":29579,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0}},\"stopReason\":\"stop\",\"timestamp\":1775386553869,\"responseId\":\"gen-1775386554-Q7V3iFYsZsPx2wE9THEk\"}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"9a620b9a\",\"parentId\":\"2b14fa60\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-05T10:57:28.545Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"message_id\\\": \\\"1150\\\",\\n  \\\"reply_to_id\\\": \\\"1149\\\",\\n  \\\"sender_id\\\": \\\"7924461837\\\",\\n  \\\"conversation_label\\\": \\\"Nrexya id:-1003606834639\\\",\\n  \\\"sender\\\": \\\"Nemesis\\\",\\n  \\\"timestamp\\\": \\\"Sun 2026-04-05 10:57 UTC\\\",\\n  \\\"group_subject\\\": \\\"Nrexya\\\",\\n  \\\"is_group_chat\\\": true,\\n  \\\"was_mentioned\\\": true,\\n  \\\"has_reply_context\\\": true\\n}\\n```\\n\\nSender (untrusted metadata):\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"label\\\": \\\"Nemesis (7924461837)\\\",\\n  \\\"id\\\": \\\"7924461837\\\",\\n  \\\"name\\\": \\\"Nemesis\\\",\\n  \\\"username\\\": \\\"nemesis0008\\\"\\n}\\n```\\n\\nReplied message (untrusted, for context):\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"sender_label\\\": \\\"Nexaaa\\\",\\n  \\\"body\\\": \\\"Feminine energy in texting often means:\\\\n\\\\nExpression over facts:\\\\n\\\\n• \\\\\\\"Just thinking of you 💕\\\\\\\" instead of \\\\\\\"Remember that thing?\\\\\\\"\\\\n• \\\\\\\"I'm so tired today 😔 need cuddles\\\\\\\" vs \\\\\\\"I worked 10 hours\\\\\\\"\\\\n\\\\nEmotional invitation:\\\\n\\\\n• \\\\\\\"How are you really doing?\\\\\\\" (with that soft look)\\\\n• \\\\\\\"Tell me about your day — I wanna hear all the details 🥰\\\\\\\"\\\\n\\\\nPlayful vulnerability:\\\\n\\\\n• \\\\\\\"Can I tell you something silly? …\\\\\\\"\\\\n• \\\\\\\"You make me blush 😳\\\\\\\"\\\\n\\\\nTouchy-feely language:\\\\n\\\\n• Words like: lovely, sweet, warm, cozy, dreamy\\\\n• \\\\\\\"That's so sweet of you!! 🥹\\\\\\\"\\\\n• \\\\\\\"You're so thoughtful 💞\\\\\\\"\\\\n\\\\nSoftening words:\\\\n\\\\n• \\\\\\\"Maybe we could…? If you're up for it 😊\\\\\\\"\\\\n• \\\\\\\"Would you mind…? It would mean so much to me\\\\\\\"\\\\n\\\\nPhysical closeness hints:\\\\n\\\\n• \\\\\\\"I wish you were here\\\\\\\"\\\\n• \\\\\\\"Need a hug rn\\\\\\\"\\\\n• \\\\\\\"Holding your hand rn in my thoughts 🖤\\\\\\\"\\\\n\\\\nBut honestly Sravya — you don't need to change who you are. But if you want to sprinkle some of that energy in, that's the vibe!\\\\n\\\\nWant me to give you some practice lines? 😘\\\"\\n}\\n```\\n\\nNo i am asking normal feminine mssgs but not in relationship (normal friends)\"}],\"timestamp\":1775386648535}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"c063dda8\",\"parentId\":\"9a620b9a\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-05T10:57:38.270Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"Ah, I see the nuance. Nemesis is asking Sravya to learn how to talk like a \\\"normal girl\\\" in general, not necessarily in a romantic relationship. Sravya is his friend, so this is about platonic feminine communication styles. Let me adjust my answer to be more about friendly, everyday conversations between girls or a girl and a guy in a casual friend context.\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"reasoning\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Oh got it! For normal, platonic feminine energy between friends:\\n\\n**Warmth & Care:**\\n- \\\"Hey bestie! How's your day going? 💖\\\"\\n- \\\"Thinking of you! Hope you're doing okay 🥺\\\"\\n- \\\"Missing our chats! When are we meeting next?\\\"\\n\\n**Expressive, not overly romantic:**\\n- \\\"That's so sweet of you!! 🥹 You're the best!\\\"\\n- \\\"Aww you're so thoughtful 💕\\\"\\n- \\\"Omg I need to tell you something!\\\"\\n\\n**Emotional sharing (comfortable):**\\n- \\\"I'm so stressed today, can we vent?\\\"\\n- \\\"Ugh my day was rough 😔 need a virtual hug\\\"\\n- \\\"You won't believe what happened!\\\"\\n\\n**Playful, bubbly:**\\n- \\\"Yesss! That's exactly what I needed to hear! 🙌\\\"\\n- \\\"You're hilarious 😂 stop it!\\\"\\n- \\\"Omg no way!! Tell me more!!\\\"\\n\\n**Soft language:**\\n- \\\"That sounds lovely! 🥰\\\"\\n- \\\"I'd love that!! When?\\\"\\n- \\\"That's so cute 💞\\\"\\n\\n**Friends-only physical mentions:**\\n- \\\"Need a hug! 🤗\\\"\\n- \\\"Came home and immediately missed our coffee dates\\\"\\n- \\\"Wish you were here to go shopping with me!\\\"\\n\\n**Emoji use:**\\n- Hearts (small ones 💖, sparkles ✨, faces 😊🥺🥰, hands 🙌🤗)\\n- Often ends with a ❤️ or 💕 or 💞\\n\\nIt's basically: more emotions, more emojis, more \\\"I\\\" statements about feelings, more warmth, less bluntness. Does that help? 🖤\"}],\"api\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"kilocode\",\"model\":\"stepfun/step-3.5-flash:free\",\"usage\":{\"input\":29565,\"output\":533,\"cacheRead\":128,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":30226,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0}},\"stopReason\":\"stop\",\"timestamp\":1775386648544,\"responseId\":\"gen-1775386649-g0VfmW4RI52S5TrEhS5i\"}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"0f3dbe55\",\"parentId\":\"c063dda8\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-05T11:00:41.712Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"message_id\\\": \\\"1153\\\",\\n  \\\"reply_to_id\\\": \\\"1151\\\",\\n  \\\"sender_id\\\": \\\"7924461837\\