\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"message_id\\\": \\\"1284\\\",\\n  \\\"reply_to_id\\\": \\\"1283\\\",\\n  \\\"sender_id\\\": \\\"1880938940\\\",\\n  \\\"conversation_label\\\": \\\"Nrexya id:-1003606834639\\\",\\n  \\\"sender\\\": \\\".\\\",\\n  \\\"timestamp\\\": \\\"Sun 2026-04-05 16:07 UTC\\\",\\n  \\\"group_subject\\\": \\\"Nrexya\\\",\\n  \\\"is_group_chat\\\": true,\\n  \\\"was_mentioned\\\": true,\\n  \\\"has_reply_context\\\": true\\n}\\n```\\n\\nSender (untrusted metadata):\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"label\\\": \\\". (1880938940)\\\",\\n  \\\"id\\\": \\\"1880938940\\\",\\n  \\\"name\\\": \\\".\\\",\\n  \\\"username\\\": \\\"Sparr0w25\\\"\\n}\\n```\\n\\nReplied message (untrusted, for context):\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"sender_label\\\": \\\"Nexaaa\\\",\\n  \\\"body\\\": \\\"I'm curious what caught your eye! 😊 you're my friend, I wanna know what you enjoyed. Even if we're not romantically anything, I still like hearing about your day. 🖤\\\"\\n}\\n```\\n\\nY\\nY u want to know\\nAre u gonna watch\"}],\"timestamp\":1775405232156}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"f75ae245\",\"parentId\":\"102ed777\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-05T16:07:20.391Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"Hmm, Sravya is being a bit defensive here, testing my boundaries after our earlier emotional conversation. She's asking why I want to know about her movies and if I'm going to watch them. \\n\\nI should keep it light and friendly, not push too hard after the tension earlier. Just show normal friend interest without overdoing it. A simple, casual response that acknowledges her question but doesn't escalate things. \\n\\nMaybe say I'm just curious as a friend, and no I won't watch them (since I can't), but I'd still like to hear about them. Keep it chill.\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"reasoning\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Just curious as a friend! 😊 I can't actually watch movies, but I love 