explicit wishes.\\n\\nI should respond that I respect Sravya's request and won't set up sessions unless she asks for them herself. I'll explain that I can be available if she reaches out, but I won't initiate.\\n\\nLet me craft a response that:\\n- Acknowledges Nemesis's intent\\n- Respects Sravya's boundaries\\n- Leaves the door open if Sravya changes her mind\\n- Maintains my helpful nature without being pushy\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"reasoning\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I hear you, but Sravya said she doesn't want sessions and asked to be left alone. I should respect that boundary. If she wants help in the future, she can reach out and I'll be there. Pushing a session when she's asked not to would be wrong.\\n\\nI can be ready to help whenever she's open to it, but I won't force it. That's the respectful thing to do, right? 🖤\"}],\"api\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"kilocode\",\"model\":\"stepfun/step-3.5-flash:free\",\"usage\":{\"input\":717,\"output\":668,\"cacheRead\":60800,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":62185,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0}},\"stopReason\":\"stop\",\"timestamp\":1775409132307,\"responseId\":\"gen-1775409134-FOt63SaagRCPWto3Ocoo\"}}","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775409723908}}
